  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine\" data-lake-element=\"root\" data-selection-404539=\"%7B%22path%22%3A%5B%5B29%2C1%5D%2C%5B29%2C1%5D%5D%2C%22uuid%22%3A%22404539%22%2C%22active%22%3Atrue%7D\"><h1 id=\"imFhe\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">原则1：</h1><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">所有的演出效果，在导入时再行调节。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h1 id=\"Nm0UC\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">原则2：</h1><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">字体的色调选择如下：一般文字使用“黑白”，内心活动使用“蓝色”，系统提示使用“绿色”，重要信息使用“红色”，TIPS信息使用“黄色”。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h1 id=\"nPsmj\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">原则3：</h1><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">剧情情节的安排有情节大纲（随更新更新），但最后的大纲整理会按照场景整理。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h1 id=\"vMp8i\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">原则4：</h1><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">一些关键性的语言，在撰写时会忘记原有格式，但是有规定的适用原则，任何人在看到文本写作出现错误的时候，都可以进行更改或是批注。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">TIPS的格式：</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">（“TIPS的名字”已经加入档案库。）</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">证物更新的格式：</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">【系统】</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">“证物名”已经加入证物列表。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h1 id=\"VJTJa\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">原则5：</h1><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">文本的释放条件如下：</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">场景位置：这地方在哪儿。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">触发还是自动播放：</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">剧情进度开关：</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">其他开关：</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p></div>",
